          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The choice of inverse kinematics, 13C beam and 6Li",
                " target, allowed measurements to be made at very low",
                " energies in the c.m. and to avoid background",
                " associated with the admixture of 12C in the 13C",
                " target.",
                "The absolute normalization of the cross section was",
                " performed by measuring the elastic scattering of",
